Python Installation:

https://youtu.be/M5ILgNI0iXw

1. Find Total Duration in Minute for each Participants 
2. Plot a Bar Chart for top 20 Students who spend most time in Class During The Session
3. Plot a Bar Chart for Bottom 20 Students who has Joined for the meeting in minutes 
4. Create a Report on of attendance out of this data having details like participant name, duration he took class, class topic name, date, total student present in class etc. 
5. Try to create a API BASED Program for automated Report Generation on single call with file (same format)

Note: Remember students join and leave the session many time, to calculate their total time in session you have to add up all that time

In [56]:
def get_minutes(time):
    """
        time = 06:48 will return time in minutes 408
        
    """
    hour, minute = time.split(':')
    hour2minute = int(hour) * 60
    minute = int(minute)
    return minute + hour2minute
In [57]:
get_minutes("06:48")
Out[57]:
408
